OL,3,CFormer D-Day pilot featured in Blind
OL,4,CVeterans UK exhibition
OL,6,FA former D-Day pilot is one of 13
OL,7,Fpartially-sighted or blind veterans
OL,8,Fwho have had their memories of VE Day
OL,9,Fbrought back to life in an exhibition.
OL,11,FCharity Blind Veterans UK has released
OL,12,Fthe illustrations, stories and
OL,13,Fphotographs as part of its After the
OL,14,FDarkness campaign, which looks to
OL,15,Frecognise their service and raise
OL,16,Ffunds for war heroes living with sight
OL,17,Floss.
