OL,6,FClaire Rowcliffe, director of
OL,7,Fengagement at Blind Veterans UK, said:
OL,8,F"As darkness descends and veterans
OL,9,Ffind themselves losing their
OL,10,Findependence, they can often feel
OL,11,Fisolated, helpless, and unable to cope.
OL,13,F"Luckily our charity is here to help
OL,14,Fthem regain their confidence and
OL,15,Findependence so they can live the
OL,16,Ffulfilled, meaningful lives they so
OL,17,Fdeserve.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
