OL,6,F"Each story is unique and not
OL,7,Fnecessarily what one would expect.
OL,8,FYes, there was joy, jubilation, and
OL,9,Fpartying in the streets, but there was
OL,10,Falso mourning for those who had been
OL,11,Flost, quickly changing societal roles,
OL,12,Fand fear of the dreaded war in the
OL,13,FPacific."
OL,15,FThe thirteen veterans' stories,
OL,16,Fillustrations, and portraits are
OL,17,Ffeatured in a special exhibition at
OL,18,FThe Cartoon Museum in London, which
OL,19,Fruns until June 29.
